data.description: Recently updated two-story, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the PNGISD area.  The upgrades, including fresh paint, new countertops, appliances, and fixtures, along with the bonus room upstairs and two new AC units, make it a promising property. There is a large den with wet bar for entertaining.  The Living/Dining room space with wood burning fireplace creates an inviting atmosphere.  This home features a large office or possible 4th bedroom.  Additionally, the large enclosed laundry room in the garage with central air, heat and a sink adds convenience.  A perfect home for a growing family designed for entertaining and family gatherings.
